            <div type="transcript" id="F513A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Spider holds a Silver Ball</l>
                    <l>In unperceived Hands - </l>
                    <l>And dancing softly<add type="alternate" extent="to Himself">as He knits</add>
 to Himself </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="His Yarn of Pearl - unwinds -">Pursues his pearly strands -</add>
His <add type="alternate" extent="Yarn">Coil</add>
Yarn of Pearl - <add type="alternate" extent="unwinds -">expends -</add>
unwinds -</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>He plies from nought to nought -</l>
                    <l>In unsubstantial Trade - </l>
                    <l>Supplants our Tapestries with His - </l>
                    <l>In half the period - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>An Hour to rear supreme </l>
                    <l>His<add type="alternate" extent="Continents">theories</add>
 Continents of Light -</l>
                    <l>Then<add type="alternate" extent="dangle from">perish by</add>
 dangle from the Housewife's<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Broom - </l>
                    <l>His<add type="alternate" extent="Boundaries -">sophistries -</add>
 Boundaries - forgot - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
